quran[24]{c,v,t,f}:
  56,88,"Ní ti ẹni tí ó bá wà nínú àwọn alásùn-únmọ́ (Wa),"
  56,89,"ìsinmi, èsè tó dára àti Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra (ni tirẹ̀)."
  56,90,"Ní ti ẹni tí ó bá wà nínú àwọn èrò ọwọ́ ọ̀tún,"
  67,28,"Sọ pé: “Ẹ sọ fún mi, tí Allāhu bá pa èmi àti àwọn tó wà pẹ̀lú mi rẹ́, tàbí tí Ó bá kẹ́ wa (ṣé ẹ lè dí I lọ́wọ́ ni?) Nítorí náà, ta ni ó máa gba àwọn aláìgbàgbọ́ là nínú ìyà ẹlẹ́ta-eléro?"
  67,29,"Sọ pé: “Òun ni Àjọkẹ́-ayé. Àwa gbà Á gbọ́. Òun sì la gbáralé. Láìpẹ́ ẹ máa mọ ta ni ó wà nínú ìṣìnà pọ́nńbélé.”"
  67,30,"Sọ pé: “Ẹ sọ fún mi, tí omi yín bá gbẹ wá, ta ni ẹni tí ó máa mú omi tó ń ṣàn wá fún yín?”{1}.",footnotes:1:Sūrah al-Mulk àti sūrah as-Sajdah jẹ́ sūrah tí Ànábì - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - máa ń ké ní alaalẹ́ ní ojoojúmọ́. Ààbò ló jẹ́ níbi ìyá nínú sàréè, gẹ́gẹ́ bí ó ṣe wà nínú hadīth Nasā’iy àti òmíràn.
  68,22,"pé ẹ jí lọ sí oko yín tí ẹ bá fẹ́ ká èso."
  68,23,"Wọ́n lọ, wọ́n sì ń fi ohùn jẹ́ẹ́jẹ́ bára wọn sọ̀rọ̀"
  68,24,"pé ní òní mẹ̀kúnnù kan kò gbọdọ̀ wọnú rẹ̀ wá ba yín."
  69,19,"Nítorí náà, ní ti ẹni tí wọ́n bá fún ní tírà rẹ̀ ní ọwọ́ ọ̀tún rẹ̀, ó máa sọ pé: “Ẹ gbà, ẹ ka tírà mi wò."
  69,20,"Dájúdájú èmi ti mọ àmọ̀dájú pé dájúdájú èmi yóò bá ìṣírò-iṣẹ́ mi pàdé.”"
  69,21,"Nítorí náà, ó máa wà nínú ìṣẹ̀mí tó máa yọ́nú sí"
  70,13,"àti àwọn ẹbí rẹ̀ tó pa tì, tí àwọn sì ń gbà á sọ́dọ̀ nílé ayé,"
  70,14,"àti gbogbo ẹni tó wà lórí ilẹ̀ ayé pátápátá, (ó máa fẹ́ fi wọ́n ṣèràpadà ẹ̀mí ara rẹ̀ níbi Ìyà). Lẹ́yìn náà, (ó máa fẹ́) kí Allāhu gba òun là (nínú ìyà Iná)."
  70,15,"Rárá! Dájúdájú (ó máa wọ) iná Laṭḥọ̄ (iná tó ń jò fòfò)."
  71,10,"Mo sì sọ pé, ẹ tọrọ àforíjìn ní ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa yín, dájúdájú Ó ń jẹ́ Aláforíjìn."
  71,11,"Ó máa rọ̀jò fún yín ní òjò púpọ̀,"
  71,12,"Ó máa fi àwọn dúkìá àti àwọn ọmọkùnrin ràn yín lọ́wọ́. Ó máa ṣe àwọn ọgbà oko fún yín. Ó sì máa ṣe àwọn odò fún yín."
  72,7,"Dájúdájú àwọn àlùjànnú lérò gẹ́gẹ́ bí ẹ̀yin ènìyàn náà ṣe lérò pé, Allāhu kò níí gbé ẹnì kan kan dìde (lẹ́yìn ikú)."
  72,8,"Dájúdájú àwa wá (ọ̀rọ̀ àyọ́gbọ́) wá sí sánmọ̀, a sì bá a tí ó ti kún fún àwọn ẹ̀ṣọ́ tó lágbára àti àwọn ògúnná."
  72,9,"Dájúdájú àwa máa ń jókòó síbẹ̀ ní àwọn ibùdó kan fún gbígbọ́ ọ̀rọ̀. Ṣùgbọ́n ẹni tó bá jọ́rọ̀ gbọ́ lásìkò yìí, ó máa rí ògúnná tó ti lúgọ dè é."
  73,1,"Ìwọ olùdaṣọbora."
  73,2,"Dìde (kírun) ní òru àyàfi fún ìgbà díẹ̀ (ni kí o fi sùn nínú òru rẹ)."
  73,3,"Lo ìlàjì rẹ̀ tàbí dín díẹ̀ kù nínú rẹ̀."